description: * OPEN HOUSE CANCELED...An OFFER has been accepted. Eastside Single-family home with lots of character, including exposed brick, recessed paneling, hardwood flooring, and high ceilings with crown moldings. This spacious and well-maintained home is conveniently located within a few blocks of the Broadway shops and the SB beaches. Other amenities include HVAC, lots of closet space, a home office, and a large rear deck. This home is a great condo alternative.
